variable.name: RACE
variable.description: NAACCR race [American Indian, Aleutian, Eskimo; Asian Indian, Pakistani; Black; Chinese; Filipino; Guamanian, NOS; Hawaiian; Korean; Other; Other Asian, incl Asian NOS and Oriental NOS; Unknown; White; Black, White]

variable.name: ETHNICITY
variable.description: NAACCR ethnicity [Mexican (incl Chicano); Non-Spanish, non-Hispanic; Other specified Spanish/Hispanic origin (includes European); Puerto Rican; South or Central American (except Brazil); Spanish NOS, Hispanic NOS, Latino NOS (based on more than just surname; Spanish surname only-no contrary evidence that the pt is not Hispanic; Unknown whether Spanish only]

variable.name: AGE_AT_DIAGNOSIS
variable.description: Age at diagnosis, rounded to the nearest year

variable.name: CNS_STATUS_AT_DIAGNOSIS
variable.description: CNS status at diagnosis [<5 CSF WBC/ul with blasts on cytospin; >5 CSF WBC/ul with blasts on cytospin and/or eye involvement, cranial nerve involvement, parenchymal brain involvement; No CNS disease]

variable.name: TESTICULAR_INVOLVEMENT
variable.description: Testicular disease status at diagnosis [Yes; No; NA / Unknown]

variable.name: MRD_DAY8
variable.description: Minimum residual disease status, in blood, day 8, 0.01% sensitivity [Positive; Negative; Unknown]

variable.name: MRD_DAY29
variable.description: Minimum residual disease status, in blood, day 29, 0.01% sensitivity [Positive; Negative; Unknown]

variable.name: YEARS_TO_EVENT
variable.description: Time to first event (or censoring), rounded to nearest 0.25 years

variable.name: YEARS_TO_DEATH
variable.description: Time to death, rounded to nearest 0.25 years
